  "title": "Marketing & Content Specialist",
  "description": "<p><strong>We're hiring a Marketing & Content Specialist at big short coffee!</strong></p><p>Check out our IG: @bigshortcoffee</p><p>In this role, you’ll craft blogs, update menus, manage our website and Google Maps, and respond to our social media DMs. You’ll work directly with the owner, wearing multiple hats in our dynamic, growing team. If you’re creative, experienced, and ready to help shape the future of coffee, please reach out to us at +6590994745 or email us at team@bigshortcoffee.com</p><p><br /><u>Job Description</u></p><ul><li>Write and publish engaging blog posts aligned with our brand voice.</li><li>Design and update in-store and digital menus.</li><li>Maintain and update the company website content.</li><li>Ensure accurate business information on Google Maps and relevant platforms.</li><li>Respond to customer queries and engage on Instagram, Xiaohongshu, Dianping, and TikTok.</li><li>Plan and coordinate photoshoots and content creation.</li><li>Collaborate with the owner on brand strategies and campaigns.</li><li>Track and report basic campaign performance.</li><li>Assist in general marketing initiatives as the brand grows.</li></ul>",
