    "description": "<p>Big Short Coffee was born to be different. While everyone’s betting on cafes in one direction; purist, specialty, exclusive, no flavors and with nothing added. We are headed in the opposite direction, like shorting the market and betting on that. We are dreamers, inventors and revolutionaries. We’re playful, inventive and full of questions.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We play with an intriguing use of premium ingredients and embrace the weird and wonderful to create coffee &amp; tea with unique, complex characters and aromas. Our Coffee Bar is built on the spirit of creativity and collaboration.</p>",
